1.) Switch to postgre froim harshitpc --> sudo -i -u postgre
2.) To enter into postgre --> psql
3.) to quit from postgre --> \q
4.) Create a new database --> createdb my_pgdb (database name)
5.) Switch between databases --> psql -d my_pgdb
6.) To show or check status of db --> conninfo
7.) To start and stop PostgreSQL server --> sudo service postgresql start/stop/status/restart
8.) To exit/logout from postgres@harshitPC --> exit (2 times)
9.) To enter into postgres cli --> psql